```

---

## 🆘 Common Issues & Solutions

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| `Cannot GET /route` | Check route definition order |
| Request body is `undefined` | Ensure `app.use(express.json())` is before routes |
| CORS errors | Install and use `cors` middleware |
| Port already in use | Change PORT or kill process: `kill -9 $(lsof -t -i:3000)` |

---

**You now have a functional Express.js REST API!** Start with this foundation and expand based on your specific requirements. Happy coding! 🚀
